      <title>印度尼西亚控制煤炭价格的举动面临中国的推动力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/indonesia-s-move-to-control-coal-prices-faces-chinese-pushback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼政府规范煤炭出口价格的计划正面临其最大客户的推动力，因为中国公司以其他供应商降低利率而支付更高的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/indonesia-s-move-to-control-coal-prices-faces-chinese-pushback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 03:58:07 GMT</pubDate>
